<p>Although Kenny Rogers gave us '<a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kn481KcjvMo&amp;feature=related" title="Kenny Rogers - The Gambler" target="_blank">The Gambler</a>' (YouTube) where he teaches us about when to 'hold em, or fold em' (the hand of life, ostensibly).  <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tony_Hsieh" title="Tony Hsieh" target="_blank">Tony Hsieh</a>, of <a href="http://zappos.com" title="Zappos" target="_blank">Zappos</a> fame, has given us another wonderful poker metaphor. Know when to change tables.</p>
